---
title: Sichuan Garlic Beef Bao Buns with Cucumber & Radish Salad
description: The hidden wonders of a bao never cease to amaze! Be dazzled with the flavour combination of garlic and Sichuan on tender beef and enjoy the crunch of the salad packed into these soft and tasty buns.
